Afrobeats super star Wizkid has informed fans that their wait it almost over as he would be releasing a new song soon. Star boy, recently announced as one of the stars headlining the 2022 Rolling Loud music festival in September for which he will earn a whooping $1million dollars (N600 million), made the announcement on his social media platforms on Friday.   Lord, help me stay away from other people’s issues…     BREAKING: PDP disqualifies two presidential aspirants     UPDATED: Tinubu, Sanwo-Olu pick APC nomination forms   Seeing the massive success of his last project “Made in Lagos”, fans and lovers of his work have continued to anticipate more pulsating music from him. The “Essence” singer also hinted the title of his new album with eyes and eagle emojis. “New music soon come and loads of it. Summer bout to be crazy,” he simply wrote.